WEBVTT

01:34.760 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:46.800 --> 01:48.480
Wen Yifan! Wen Yifan!

01:48.560 --> 01:50.680
Your mom called and asked you
to go to the hospital now.

01:50.760 --> 01:51.640
Your dad is--

01:51.720 --> 01:52.840
Be careful!

01:53.360 --> 01:54.680
Stay safe!

02:17.280 --> 02:19.560
Sorry. The subscriber you dialed

02:19.640 --> 02:21.440
cannot be connected for the moment.

02:21.520 --> 02:22.480
Please dial later.

02:22.560 --> 02:24.840
Sorry. The subscriber you dialed

02:24.920 --> 02:26.360
cannot be connected for the moment.

02:26.440 --> 02:27.960
Please redial later.

02:35.720 --> 02:37.960
Sorry. The subscriber you dialed

02:38.040 --> 02:39.720
cannot be connected for the moment.

02:39.800 --> 02:41.120
Please dial later.

02:52.960 --> 02:53.800
Thanks.

03:11.800 --> 03:12.680
Why are you here?

03:15.040 --> 03:16.360
I don't feel like going to school

03:17.960 --> 03:19.760
and want to know
what it feels like to skip classes.

04:48.720 --> 04:49.880
I will always be with you,

04:52.000 --> 04:52.880
no matter what.

05:48.120 --> 05:48.960
3,079 DAYS

05:49.040 --> 05:52.440
THE 17TH DAY OF OFFICIALLY LIVING TOGETHER

05:52.520 --> 05:53.960
Anyway, in conclusion,

05:54.040 --> 05:57.480
everyone's work
has been fairly good this year.

05:58.000 --> 05:59.320
It's just barely passing, though.

06:00.480 --> 06:02.840
I hope everyone will continue
to strive hard next year.

06:05.000 --> 06:07.640
It's time for the most troublesome issue
of the year again.

06:10.160 --> 06:12.840
Who will be on duty
during the Spring Festival?

06:16.240 --> 06:19.800
Is there any volunteer
who will impress me?

06:25.400 --> 06:26.560
You all keep silent?

06:27.240 --> 06:29.880
Okay. Then I'll call names.

06:32.080 --> 06:33.200
Su Tian?

06:33.280 --> 06:36.080
Ms. Qian, I…

06:37.040 --> 06:38.880
Oh, right. I forgot.

06:38.960 --> 06:40.200
Take a good rest then.

06:40.280 --> 06:41.440
Thank you, Ms. Qian.

06:44.800 --> 06:46.040
Zhen Yu,

06:46.120 --> 06:48.280
I remember that you are from Nanwu.

06:48.360 --> 06:50.960
So, you don't have to go out of town.
Could you stay on duty?

06:51.040 --> 06:53.080
Mr. Qian, I bought
the ticket to Hainan long ago

06:53.160 --> 06:54.600
and will celebrate
the Spring Festival there.

06:54.680 --> 06:55.720
I've even bought some dresses.

06:55.800 --> 06:57.920
You are going to celebrate
the Spring Festival in Hainan?

06:58.000 --> 06:59.560
You are really rich.

06:59.640 --> 07:01.000
I bought it long ago.
It was not expensive.

07:04.120 --> 07:06.280
Fu Zhuang, stop hiding.

07:06.360 --> 07:08.080
I've seen you.

07:08.160 --> 07:10.720
Ms. Qian, I… I have been
out of home for two years.

07:11.320 --> 07:13.720
- Stay with your mother then.
- Thank you, Ms. Qian.

07:13.800 --> 07:14.640
Wu Mian?

07:15.720 --> 07:18.920
Ms. Qian, I have to go home
for a blind date this year.

07:19.000 --> 07:20.280
My mom has arranged it for me.

07:20.360 --> 07:21.360
I won't be back until the eighth day
of the Spring Festival.

07:21.440 --> 07:22.280
Just lock the door.

07:22.360 --> 07:24.720
Help finish the food
in the refrigerator. Thanks.

07:27.800 --> 07:29.000
Ms. Qian,

07:29.080 --> 07:31.840
I can stay on duty.
I don't have anything else to do anyway.

07:32.960 --> 07:34.120
You see?

07:34.200 --> 07:37.800
Look how responsible Yifan is!
You guys need to learn from her.

07:39.120 --> 07:40.480
Thank you for your hard work, Yifan.

07:43.640 --> 07:45.400
Okay, stop working.

07:45.480 --> 07:47.080
Everyone is so busy.

07:49.440 --> 07:50.920
You are not going home
for the Spring Festival?

07:52.800 --> 07:53.880
Su Haoan!

07:54.920 --> 07:57.280
Where are you, Su Haoan? Su Haoan!

07:58.040 --> 07:59.600
Su Haoan!

08:00.760 --> 08:01.760
Come here!

08:07.040 --> 08:08.360
What orders did you place?

08:10.520 --> 08:13.080
- What's wrong?
- Why did you keep sending me orders?

08:13.160 --> 08:15.200
GO HOME WITH SU HAOAN
DURING THE SPRING FESTIVAL

08:15.280 --> 08:16.440
Don't you take all kinds of orders?

08:16.520 --> 08:19.160
Of course not! What else do you want me
to do except have dinner?

08:20.440 --> 08:21.920
You can pretend to be my girlfriend.

08:23.440 --> 08:25.480
Pretend to be your girlfriend?

08:25.560 --> 08:26.760
Our platform strictly prohibits
pornography, gambling, and--

08:28.920 --> 08:31.600
You guys just go on.
Keep on eating and drinking.

08:31.680 --> 08:32.600
It's fine.

08:33.440 --> 08:34.280
- What's fine?
- We haven't seen

08:34.360 --> 08:36.000
each other for a long time.
Why are you talking so loudly?

08:36.080 --> 08:37.400
Where are we going?

08:37.480 --> 08:38.919
Let's go upstairs and talk about it.

08:41.000 --> 08:42.880
- Take your seat.
- Tell me.

08:43.640 --> 08:45.800
Drink some water first. Don't be mad.

08:45.880 --> 08:47.000
Tell me now!

08:47.080 --> 08:49.480
Here's the thing.
My grandpa and grandma had a fight.

08:49.560 --> 08:50.680
My grandma went
on a self-driving tour out of anger

08:50.760 --> 08:52.440
and it has been for almost a year.

08:52.520 --> 08:55.040
She said she wouldn't be home
for the Spring Festival

08:55.120 --> 08:56.200
if I didn't bring home a girlfriend.

08:56.280 --> 08:57.840
- So, I'm wondering--
- I won't play.

08:57.920 --> 08:58.720
I didn't finish.

08:58.800 --> 09:00.080
You want me to pretend
to be your lover, right?

09:00.160 --> 09:01.120
- Yes.
- I won't accept it.

09:01.200 --> 09:02.720
- Why?
- It's awkward.

09:02.800 --> 09:04.520
Because I never take a job
of pretending to be someone's girlfriend.

09:04.600 --> 09:06.360
Just help me, as I'm your best friend.

09:06.440 --> 09:07.800
It's awkward because it's you.

09:10.400 --> 09:11.680
So, you can do it for someone else?

09:24.800 --> 09:25.720
Here, look!

09:28.840 --> 09:31.560
- Who's J?
- It's Jun.

09:31.640 --> 09:32.480
He's a chef.

09:32.560 --> 09:33.840
"Someone else" doesn't mean

09:33.920 --> 09:35.520
I can do it
if someone else places the order.

09:35.600 --> 09:36.440
Then who should place the order?

09:36.520 --> 09:37.640
It requires me to pretend
to be your girlfriend anyway.

09:37.720 --> 09:39.880
You said you could do it for someone else.

09:39.960 --> 09:43.040
You will have my account blocked
for brushing scams

09:43.120 --> 09:44.960
by doing this. Cancel them now!

09:48.280 --> 09:50.360
Well, guys, cancel the order
if you have placed one.

09:51.240 --> 09:52.360
Don't place any orders if you haven't yet.

09:52.440 --> 09:54.200
I'll still treat you to drinks. Thanks.

09:56.000 --> 09:58.480
Let's make it clear
that I'll help you as a friend.

09:58.560 --> 10:00.040
But I won't do anything
only a girlfriend can do.

10:00.640 --> 10:02.080
Okay. I won't do anything
like that either.

10:02.160 --> 10:04.440
Come on. Let's go downstairs.
I'll treat you to drinks and food.

10:05.040 --> 10:06.960
It's my apology. Let's go.

10:10.040 --> 10:11.120
Come on.

10:11.200 --> 10:12.440
- What?
- Didn't I say I couldn't?

10:13.240 --> 10:14.080
Excuse me!

10:19.000 --> 10:23.160
Five, four, three, two, one!

10:26.840 --> 10:27.960
- Are you okay?
- Yes.

10:28.040 --> 10:30.440
Who wants a red envelope?

10:31.000 --> 10:32.200
- Here!
- Come on!

10:32.280 --> 10:34.400
- Come on!
- Happy New Year!

10:34.480 --> 10:36.160
Come on! Here! You two take these.

10:36.240 --> 10:38.120
- I'll grab some more.
- Thank you.

10:38.640 --> 10:39.800
You are welcome.

10:39.880 --> 10:41.800
Don't hustle. Be careful.

10:41.880 --> 10:43.040
Yifan,

10:43.120 --> 10:44.560
can you do it on your own?

10:44.640 --> 10:47.320
I can be here at any time if you need me.

10:47.400 --> 10:49.480
Don't worry, Tian.
Just go back for the Spring Festival.

10:49.560 --> 10:52.000
Your baby needs to rest even if you don't.

10:54.800 --> 10:57.840
I left the baby's father but kept the baby
and will be a single mother.

10:58.680 --> 11:01.520
I don't know whether my decision
is right or wrong.

11:02.280 --> 11:04.720
Or is all of this an arbitrary act?

11:06.600 --> 11:08.000
Do you think my kid

11:08.080 --> 11:09.760
will ask me where their dad is
in the future Spring Festivals?

11:12.040 --> 11:14.080
Don't think too much.

11:14.160 --> 11:16.280
Children nowadays
are much more open-minded than us.

11:17.080 --> 11:20.040
Also, the vision of love now is different.

11:22.440 --> 11:23.360
Don't cry.

11:23.440 --> 11:25.480
I am touched by you.

11:26.720 --> 11:27.720
I believe

11:27.800 --> 11:30.200
you will bring a bright future
for the baby.

11:31.000 --> 11:33.080
- That's for sure.
- Don't cry.

11:33.840 --> 11:35.920
Come on! I'm back.

11:36.000 --> 11:37.880
Here. Why are you crying?

11:37.960 --> 11:40.200
I'm moved by what you did.

11:40.280 --> 11:41.800
Look at you. Is someone bullying you?

11:41.880 --> 11:43.080
No.

11:43.160 --> 11:44.560
This is for the baby.

11:45.600 --> 11:47.480
- Thank you.
- Yifan,

11:47.560 --> 11:48.720
thank you for staying on duty.

11:48.800 --> 11:51.160
Be happy every day in the coming year.

11:51.800 --> 11:52.840
Thank you.

12:00.200 --> 12:03.360
AUSPICIOUSNESS FROM THE GOLDEN LOONG

12:03.440 --> 12:06.520
BLESSINGS FOR THE NEW YEAR

12:06.600 --> 12:09.200
HAPPY NEW YEAR

12:20.480 --> 12:22.720
HAPPY NEW YEAR

12:25.200 --> 12:26.680
You didn't go home, Mr. Zhang?

12:27.200 --> 12:28.160
Why did you leave so late?

12:29.480 --> 12:30.440
I'm on duty.

12:30.520 --> 12:31.680
Will you still be here in a few days?

12:31.760 --> 12:33.440
I will. Knock on my door if you need help.

12:33.520 --> 12:35.040
You won't go home
for the Spring Festival either?

12:35.120 --> 12:37.160
Someone has to guard the TV station.

12:37.240 --> 12:38.640
It's hard to be on duty alone.

12:39.160 --> 12:41.280
- Take this.
- You are too kind.

12:41.360 --> 12:42.200
Just take it.

12:42.280 --> 12:45.120
Dad, when will jiaozi be ready?
I'm hungry.

12:45.200 --> 12:46.600
Be a good girl and check it yourself.

12:48.520 --> 12:49.840
I am not alone.

12:49.920 --> 12:52.720
My wife and daughter
came from our hometown to stay with me.

12:53.480 --> 12:56.600
About this, madam,
just keep it for yourself.

12:56.680 --> 12:59.040
No need to be polite with me.
Keep it for the kid.

13:00.320 --> 13:01.360
Here.

13:01.440 --> 13:04.040
Jelly! My favorite!

13:04.120 --> 13:05.200
Thank you.

13:06.640 --> 13:07.840
Come in and have some jiaozi.

13:07.920 --> 13:09.480
No, thanks. I have things to do.

13:09.560 --> 13:10.880
Okay. Happy New Year!

13:11.480 --> 13:12.520
Happy New Year!

13:16.480 --> 13:18.520
Here, your favorite grape flavor.

13:22.960 --> 13:24.280
Zhang, try one.

13:27.600 --> 13:28.920
Let's eat jiaozi!

13:54.680 --> 13:57.240
- Are you ready?
- Yes!

13:57.320 --> 13:58.360
Wait a moment.

14:00.320 --> 14:02.000
The wine is ready.

14:02.080 --> 14:04.800
The ceremony is about to begin.
Raise your glass.

14:05.520 --> 14:08.000
One, two, three…

14:08.600 --> 14:09.440
Cheers!

14:09.520 --> 14:12.400
- Happy New Year!
- Happy New Year!

14:13.920 --> 14:14.840
Happy New Year, Dian!

14:15.720 --> 14:16.840
Happy New Year, Dian!

14:16.920 --> 14:17.880
Happy New Year!

14:17.960 --> 14:19.880
- Why is Yifan alone?
- Well, Grandpa…

14:22.400 --> 14:26.320
Welcome to the Spring Festival Gala
group chat conference.

14:28.600 --> 14:29.640
Dian,

14:30.680 --> 14:31.880
say hello to Qiao.

14:31.960 --> 14:34.920
- Happy New Year, Dian!
- Happy New Year!

15:06.880 --> 15:08.520
Is it that funny?

15:08.600 --> 15:11.880
It depends on the audience's mood
whether the sketch is funny or not.

15:11.960 --> 15:13.360
You should be happy
for the Spring Festival.

15:30.080 --> 15:32.160
Qiao, come eat jiaozi.

15:32.240 --> 15:33.120
Thank you, Grandma.

15:34.240 --> 15:35.880
Did you eat jiaozi, Dian?

15:35.960 --> 15:37.200
Not yet.

15:37.280 --> 15:39.080
You have to eat jiaozi
for the Spring Festival.

15:39.160 --> 15:40.760
Will you cook some yourself
or order a takeaway?

15:40.840 --> 15:42.080
We're going to set off firecrackers.

15:42.160 --> 15:44.680
Hurry up, Qiao!
Let's go out to set off firecrackers.

15:44.760 --> 15:46.480
I'm going to set off firecrackers now.

15:46.560 --> 15:47.760
Talk to you later. Bye!

15:57.440 --> 16:00.480
Jiaozi, the taste of reunion.

16:01.480 --> 16:03.400
I forgot to buy jiaozi.

16:30.480 --> 16:31.680
Why are you back?

16:32.920 --> 16:34.200
Didn't you tell me you wouldn't be back

16:34.280 --> 16:35.120
until the eighth day
of the Spring Festival?

16:35.960 --> 16:38.160
Too many relatives at home.
There are not enough rooms.

16:41.680 --> 16:44.960
- Happy New Year!
- Happy New Year!

16:45.960 --> 16:48.120
It's mine! What are you doing?

17:00.800 --> 17:03.120
Come home for dinner! What time is it?

17:03.840 --> 17:05.160
Will you have
the Spring Festival Eve's dinner or not?

17:26.599 --> 17:28.000
Didn't you have
the Spring Festival Eve's dinner?

18:05.400 --> 18:06.240
Wen Yifan.

18:14.480 --> 18:15.320
What's wrong?

18:17.280 --> 18:18.200
I cooked too much.

18:19.000 --> 18:19.840
Help eat some.

18:24.720 --> 18:26.560
I'll help you put the rest
in the refrigerator.

18:35.720 --> 18:36.640
Leave the vegetables here.

18:37.600 --> 18:39.360
The meatballs… Won't you eat them?

18:40.440 --> 18:42.320
Put some in if you want to eat them.

18:43.080 --> 18:43.960
Okay.

18:50.560 --> 18:52.760
Should we put in some jiaozi?
It's the Spring Festival Eve.

18:55.400 --> 18:56.280
Okay.

18:57.200 --> 18:58.280
Then put some in.

18:59.760 --> 19:00.840
Give me two eggs.

19:09.920 --> 19:12.000
Did you put in a whole pack of noodles?

19:13.040 --> 19:13.920
So?

19:18.200 --> 19:20.400
I probably can't help you with too much.

19:21.200 --> 19:22.080
What?

19:22.960 --> 19:24.160
I'm not very hungry.

19:24.960 --> 19:25.840
I know.

19:33.160 --> 19:34.000
The noodles you cooked

19:38.720 --> 19:39.760
are pretty tasty.

19:43.440 --> 19:46.480
Your expression
will make people think I intoxicated you.

19:49.040 --> 19:50.760
I didn't know you could cook.

19:51.520 --> 19:53.160
Is there anything I can't do?

19:53.800 --> 19:55.440
- Aren't there a lot?
- Such as?

19:56.440 --> 19:57.400
Such as

19:59.400 --> 20:00.880
cooking noodles for just one person.

20:07.760 --> 20:09.680
Aren't you hungry? Why don't you eat?

20:11.360 --> 20:12.320
I'll eat later.

20:26.800 --> 20:29.840
It's a little weird
for you to stare at me while I eat.

20:32.200 --> 20:35.480
It's the Spring Festival Eve today.
So, it should be a reunion dinner.

20:35.560 --> 20:36.640
We should eat together.

20:58.440 --> 20:59.960
Do you have a name for the noodles?

21:04.360 --> 21:06.400
Noodles of wealth, longevity,

21:07.920 --> 21:08.760
and richness.

21:11.200 --> 21:12.440
No wonder there is jiaozi.

21:19.920 --> 21:22.600
Thanks to you, I'm having jiaozi.

21:26.520 --> 21:28.720
Today, Sang Yan and I

21:29.280 --> 21:31.560
have our first dinner together alone
after our reunion.

21:43.840 --> 21:45.480
The Spring Festival Gala has young faces.

21:54.320 --> 21:56.120
So, whether the show is good or not

21:56.200 --> 21:57.800
depends on whom you watch the show with.

22:12.560 --> 22:17.880
HAPPY NEW YEAR

22:23.560 --> 22:24.600
ZHAO YUANDONG INVITES YOU TO A VIDEO CALL

22:29.000 --> 22:29.920
Jiang.

22:30.640 --> 22:34.200
Happy New Year! Did you eat?

22:35.320 --> 22:36.360
Yes.

22:39.440 --> 22:40.680
I had jiaozi.

22:41.600 --> 22:42.760
Jia,

22:43.360 --> 22:44.600
say hello to Jiang.

22:48.520 --> 22:49.800
There were years when I didn't even know

22:49.880 --> 22:51.040
what the meaning
of the Spring Festival was.

22:52.040 --> 22:54.640
I made a lot of dishes
for the Spring Festival Eve.

22:54.720 --> 22:56.080
Taste these.

22:56.160 --> 22:58.200
Eat as much as you can. There are more.

22:58.280 --> 23:00.880
More dishes are to be served.
Eat as much as you can, Jia.

23:00.960 --> 23:03.000
Eat some more, Fan. Eat the dishes.

23:05.520 --> 23:07.760
It's my house. I have the final say!

23:07.840 --> 23:10.400
I don't want her to eat at the table!

23:11.760 --> 23:14.880
What did you promise me?
Can't you just bear with it a bit?

23:16.800 --> 23:19.600
Fan, just eat.

23:25.080 --> 23:27.440
Zheng, say hello to Jiang.

23:28.280 --> 23:29.480
Hello, Fan.

23:30.280 --> 23:31.240
Hello.

23:31.840 --> 23:33.560
Well, say a little more.

23:34.520 --> 23:36.560
Fan, Happy New Year.

23:36.640 --> 23:39.240
Come home when you are free.

23:40.160 --> 23:41.200
Yeah.

23:43.480 --> 23:46.640
Jiang, were you at work during the day?

23:46.720 --> 23:48.880
You must be tired. Go to bed early.

23:48.960 --> 23:50.520
I'll hang up now. Bye.

24:08.520 --> 24:10.120
Why didn't you

24:10.880 --> 24:13.160
wish your parents a happy new year?

24:19.560 --> 24:21.200
Isn't it always like this?

24:22.080 --> 24:23.520
My parents don't care much about me.

24:58.040 --> 24:59.640
I fell asleep accidentally.

25:03.240 --> 25:04.680
Did they sing "Unforgettable Tonight"?

25:07.000 --> 25:08.000
The chorus is coming soon.

25:09.760 --> 25:10.600
Do you want to sing together?

25:12.400 --> 25:14.000
Okay. You go first.

25:14.920 --> 25:16.000
You wish!

25:24.480 --> 25:25.720
Dian.

25:26.960 --> 25:27.840
Come on. Time for bed.

25:31.640 --> 25:32.760
I'm going to bed now.

25:34.200 --> 25:35.040
Good night.

25:45.680 --> 25:46.680
Happy New Year.

25:56.320 --> 25:57.320
Happy New Year.

26:16.400 --> 26:19.760
You uncle doesn't have a son.

26:19.840 --> 26:20.680
Enough.

26:24.560 --> 26:25.520
Jiang.

26:27.280 --> 26:28.200
Jiang.

26:30.720 --> 26:33.440
MEMORIAL TABLET OF MY FATHER WEN LIANGZHE

26:44.240 --> 26:45.280
Don't be too sad.

26:53.680 --> 26:55.200
What's your arrangement

26:56.080 --> 26:58.200
for Yifan in the future?

27:07.160 --> 27:11.160
Could you please let her live with you?

27:11.240 --> 27:12.840
How about asking her
to live with your mother-in-law?

27:12.920 --> 27:14.280
After all, she's her grandma.
What do you think?

27:15.240 --> 27:18.520
You're still young.
It's not easy to take a child with you.

27:19.720 --> 27:21.400
Think about it, won't you?

28:02.320 --> 28:04.120
- Grandma!
- Yifan!

28:07.200 --> 28:09.000
I'll pick you up when I settle down.

28:35.320 --> 28:37.760
Shuangjiang, your grandma
can't look after you in the future.

28:37.840 --> 28:39.680
Come live with me.

28:52.080 --> 28:53.760
Jiang, come on. Time for lunch.

28:55.840 --> 28:59.440
If you don't want to live with me,
call your mother frequently

28:59.520 --> 29:01.240
and ask her
to pick you up soon, all right?

29:01.320 --> 29:02.720
Mom! Mom!

29:33.160 --> 29:38.080
BRAISED FOOD

29:43.240 --> 29:44.440
Hi. Twenty yuan.

29:47.880 --> 29:48.720
Twenty.

29:49.840 --> 29:51.920
Where is the money my aunt gave me?

29:52.480 --> 29:55.400
Will you buy it or not?
People are waiting in line.

29:57.840 --> 30:00.040
I'm sorry. My money seems to be lost.

30:02.200 --> 30:03.480
How could it be lost?

30:04.880 --> 30:07.000
Will I be sent to somewhere else again?

30:27.800 --> 30:29.160
Wen Shuangjiang.

30:30.840 --> 30:32.080
What are you doing sitting here?

30:42.760 --> 30:45.040
Why are you wearing this expression?

30:51.440 --> 30:53.080
Can you lend me 20 yuan?

31:01.280 --> 31:04.120
I came to play basketball
and didn't bring any money.

31:05.400 --> 31:08.080
- Don't bother.
- Bother with what?

31:09.400 --> 31:10.440
That I don't have money now

31:10.520 --> 31:12.200
doesn't mean I won't have money
in five minutes.

31:13.040 --> 31:13.920
Take it.

31:15.600 --> 31:16.640
Take it.

31:19.200 --> 31:20.960
Wait for me here. Five minutes.

31:21.040 --> 31:22.800
Just five minutes. Wait for me.

31:44.680 --> 31:45.520
Here.

31:49.640 --> 31:50.680
Take it.

31:52.120 --> 31:54.240
You can give it back when you want.

31:55.080 --> 31:55.960
Thank you.

31:57.600 --> 31:58.520
What?

31:59.600 --> 32:00.920
It looks like you are about to cry.

32:03.760 --> 32:05.000
You don't have to be so touched.

32:06.200 --> 32:07.880
Well, it's not a big deal.

32:08.440 --> 32:09.880
It's just that you lost 20 yuan.

32:11.240 --> 32:12.880
Just call me

32:13.760 --> 32:14.880
if you lose money again.

32:29.680 --> 32:31.000
I can lend you

32:32.640 --> 32:33.720
however much you want.

33:11.960 --> 33:12.800
Coming.

33:18.000 --> 33:18.840
Qiao?

33:18.920 --> 33:20.680
- Dian!
- Xiang Lang?

33:20.760 --> 33:22.480
Happy New Year!

33:22.560 --> 33:25.600
Happy New Year, Dian!

33:27.840 --> 33:29.200
Long time no see.

33:29.280 --> 33:31.520
See? We are here to wish you a happy
new year on the first day of the year.

33:31.600 --> 33:32.680
- Are you surprised?
- Are you shocked?

33:32.760 --> 33:34.160
I'm surprised and shocked.

33:34.240 --> 33:35.320
- Please come in.
- Okay.

33:36.080 --> 33:37.440
This is Dian's new home.

33:38.760 --> 33:40.160
Is this Sang Yan's room?

33:40.680 --> 33:43.320
Qiao! Qiao, this is someone else's room.
Let's not go in.

33:43.400 --> 33:45.000
Why are you so nervous?

33:45.960 --> 33:47.920
We… We have an agreement

33:48.000 --> 33:49.560
to tell each other in advance
if people come over.

33:50.240 --> 33:51.760
We are other people?

33:53.560 --> 33:55.160
Look, I bought you a New Year's gift.

33:55.240 --> 33:56.560
We often fought over it when we were kids.

33:56.640 --> 33:59.480
She saw this at the store downstairs
and couldn't even walk.

33:59.560 --> 34:01.080
I knew she wanted to eat this.

34:01.160 --> 34:02.360
Not like that!
It's the first day of the Spring Festival.

34:02.440 --> 34:04.320
I'm bringing love home…

34:04.400 --> 34:07.640
- To share it.
- You two are so harmonious now.

34:07.720 --> 34:09.320
- Give it to me! Come on.
- Let's go.

34:11.560 --> 34:13.719
I need to use the bathroom, Dian.

34:13.800 --> 34:16.080
It's Sang Yan's. Go to the one in my room.

34:16.159 --> 34:18.360
I'll use Sang Yan's.
We are both boys. He won't mind.

34:19.199 --> 34:20.679
He will.

34:21.320 --> 34:22.480
Here, eat this.

34:27.360 --> 34:29.639
Do you have poker cards? Let's play poker!

34:29.719 --> 34:30.920
I'll get them.

34:32.440 --> 34:33.719
Wait a minute. I need to answer a call.

34:33.800 --> 34:35.400
Where are they? I'll get them.

34:37.560 --> 34:38.800
There,

34:38.880 --> 34:41.040
in my dressing table drawer.

34:41.120 --> 34:41.960
Okay.

34:47.560 --> 34:48.440
Hello?

34:49.239 --> 34:51.280
- You are awake?
- What are you calling me for?

34:51.360 --> 34:53.360
I bought too much porridge this morning.

34:53.440 --> 34:55.199
It's in the rice cooker. Eat some.

34:57.120 --> 34:58.560
I didn't know Sang Yan was so neat.

34:58.640 --> 34:59.480
The bathroom is neatly arranged.

35:05.200 --> 35:06.040
Dian,

35:07.000 --> 35:08.800
I can't find the poker cards.
Look for them.

35:08.880 --> 35:10.000
Okay, I'll get them for you later.

35:10.600 --> 35:11.640
There are other people.

35:11.720 --> 35:13.600
Yes. Well, Qiao came
to wish me a happy new year.

35:13.680 --> 35:15.680
You called me
when I was about to call you.

35:15.760 --> 35:17.200
There's a guy too.

35:19.040 --> 35:20.200
Xiang Lang is here too.

35:22.600 --> 35:23.640
Eat this.

35:25.640 --> 35:26.720
Hello? Are you listening?

35:28.640 --> 35:30.400
It's too noisy here. I can't hear clearly.

35:31.040 --> 35:32.200
Talk later when I'm back.

35:32.880 --> 35:33.960
Hello?

35:39.720 --> 35:41.040
Is it noisy?

35:42.720 --> 35:43.680
I'm dead!

35:52.320 --> 35:54.200
What should I do?
He's killing his way back!

35:56.840 --> 35:59.000
Aren't we supposed to watch movies
and play cards at home?

35:59.080 --> 36:01.080
Where are we going when it's so cold?

36:02.800 --> 36:03.840
Dian?

36:05.400 --> 36:07.400
We should take a walk outside
during the festival.

36:11.040 --> 36:12.920
Anyway, I haven't been home
for a long time

36:13.520 --> 36:14.960
and want to take a walk.

36:15.040 --> 36:17.360
How about going somewhere far away?

36:17.440 --> 36:18.680
Good!

36:18.760 --> 36:20.920
But I can't go home too late.

36:22.560 --> 36:25.000
Dian, something's wrong with you.

36:25.080 --> 36:27.960
- Are you afraid of Sang Yan?
- What does it have to do with Sang Yan?

36:28.560 --> 36:31.800
One thing in the joint rental agreement
between Dian and Sang Yan

36:31.880 --> 36:33.280
is they can't take friends home for fun.

36:33.360 --> 36:35.640
- And they can't go home too late.
- Don't exaggerate.

36:38.120 --> 36:40.920
Is Sang Yan usually very fierce to you?

36:41.000 --> 36:44.160
- Why do I feel you fear him?
- No, don't listen to Qiao's exaggeration.

36:44.240 --> 36:46.000
Why should I fear him?

36:46.080 --> 36:48.040
If it's not fear,

36:48.120 --> 36:49.720
it's… care?

36:51.280 --> 36:53.240
Anyway, what we are doing is quite fun.

36:53.320 --> 36:55.440
It's like we are playing PVP in a game

36:55.520 --> 36:57.800
and we keep provoking our opponent.

36:57.880 --> 37:00.280
Then he got angry and picked up the sword.

37:00.960 --> 37:02.040
SWEEPING THOUSANDS OF TROOPS

37:05.400 --> 37:07.240
Since we're running for life, sit down.

37:07.840 --> 37:09.920
- Let's escape from that big monster.
- Okay.

37:15.040 --> 37:16.200
You've driven for so long.

37:16.280 --> 37:18.000
Is this the splendid scenery
you talked about?

37:18.080 --> 37:19.600
I've been here when I was a kid.

37:20.600 --> 37:21.920
It is beautiful.

37:22.000 --> 37:25.240
It's so cold. The coldness
is giving me a headache.

37:30.560 --> 37:31.880
I think it's beautiful.

37:32.760 --> 37:33.760
Do you know

37:33.840 --> 37:36.080
legend has it there is a fairy?

37:36.160 --> 37:38.320
She can make your wish come true
if you make a wish.

37:38.920 --> 37:40.520
- Where is she?
- Over there.

37:41.400 --> 37:42.480
In the illusory.

37:45.880 --> 37:46.720
I need to answer a call.

37:48.040 --> 37:49.040
You are busy even in the Spring Festival.

37:50.480 --> 37:51.400
I have an order.

37:51.920 --> 37:54.360
It's not easy for us to meet.
You should have turned it off.

37:54.960 --> 37:56.200
I took the order
before the Spring Festival.

37:56.280 --> 37:57.400
I'll answer it.

38:06.920 --> 38:07.800
Dian,

38:08.880 --> 38:09.880
what's your wish?

38:16.720 --> 38:20.040
Forget it. No wish can be truly realized.

38:25.120 --> 38:26.520
- Hello?
- Hello?

38:26.600 --> 38:29.800
Zhong Siqiao, I was wondering
if we should rehearse for it.

38:29.880 --> 38:33.400
- Rehearse?
- More like a discussion.

38:36.400 --> 38:38.800
Isn't it just helping you
by having dinner with you?

38:38.880 --> 38:39.880
Please!

38:40.600 --> 38:42.400
- Where are you?
- At work.

38:43.080 --> 38:44.680
Okay, I got it.

38:44.760 --> 38:45.840
Okay, it's a deal. Bye.

38:47.920 --> 38:49.440
- You don't have to.
- It's fine.

38:50.680 --> 38:51.600
Put it on.

39:05.160 --> 39:06.240
I'm leaving.

39:09.360 --> 39:11.480
- Did you catch a cold?
- Seems like it.

39:11.560 --> 39:13.240
I said you caught a cold
and you didn't believe it.

39:14.080 --> 39:15.040
Here, take the cold medicine.

39:15.840 --> 39:17.160
Thank you.

39:17.720 --> 39:18.960
- Take it when you are back.
- Okay.

39:20.160 --> 39:21.640
You are only here to take an order?

39:21.720 --> 39:23.040
Yes, the client made an appointment
to discuss it here.

39:24.280 --> 39:26.480
- Remember to take medicine.
- OK, stay safe.

39:26.560 --> 39:27.480
- Bye.
- Bye.

39:27.560 --> 39:28.600
Bye.

39:47.240 --> 39:48.760
UPTOWN FLOWER CITY

39:48.840 --> 39:51.760
- Hello, Qiao?
- You arrived home so early?

39:52.360 --> 39:54.400
We just arrived.
I'm still in Xiang Lang's car.

39:55.800 --> 39:57.480
Did you go somewhere else?

39:59.720 --> 40:00.800
Well…

40:01.880 --> 40:03.040
What do you want to say?

40:04.240 --> 40:07.040
Can you please help me check
if Sang Yan is still working?

40:10.240 --> 40:11.920
He doesn't seem to be here.

40:12.720 --> 40:13.680
What's wrong?

40:13.760 --> 40:15.280
You are afraid to meet him
when you are back home.

40:15.360 --> 40:16.440
Of course not.

40:17.120 --> 40:18.520
Okay, that's it.

40:20.000 --> 40:21.200
Shall I go upstairs with you?

40:22.480 --> 40:24.040
Let's go eat something. Are you hungry?

40:25.560 --> 40:27.480
Well, Qiao, we are going to eat something.

40:27.560 --> 40:28.880
Take time with your work.

40:29.760 --> 40:32.760
Okay. Then you go and eat. Bye!

40:32.840 --> 40:34.040
Okay, bye.

40:34.720 --> 40:35.920
Let's go eat casserole porridge.

40:36.000 --> 40:37.520
We've been in the cold the whole day.
It will warm us.

40:40.080 --> 40:41.280
You are awake?

40:41.360 --> 40:42.400
What are you calling me for?

40:42.480 --> 40:44.280
I bought too much porridge this morning.

40:44.360 --> 40:46.040
It's in the rice cooker. Help eat some.

40:46.640 --> 40:48.280
Oh, no! The porridge!

40:48.960 --> 40:50.640
We can eat something else
if you don't want it.

40:50.720 --> 40:52.880
It's not that.
We'll eat it some other day.

40:52.960 --> 40:55.040
- Be careful on the road.
- Dian…

40:56.680 --> 41:00.480
UPTOWN FLOWER CITY

41:27.320 --> 41:28.400
What are you looking for?

41:30.520 --> 41:31.760
You're back.

41:33.040 --> 41:34.000
I was back at noon.

41:36.280 --> 41:39.120
I'm sorry. I forgot to eat
the porridge you asked me to.

41:39.640 --> 41:40.560
Why did you apologize?

41:42.240 --> 41:44.760
Do you think I bought
the porridge for you especially?

41:50.040 --> 41:52.200
Who took off gloves to insist

41:52.280 --> 41:53.840
that we can't bring other people home?

41:54.960 --> 41:56.000
Who was it?

41:58.600 --> 42:00.760
I'm sorry.
I'll tell you in advance next time.

42:00.840 --> 42:01.760
Next time?

42:05.200 --> 42:07.200
Do you want to punish me?

42:10.920 --> 42:12.080
Okay, punishment.

42:13.120 --> 42:14.640
So, what will the punishment be?

42:18.560 --> 42:19.720
I don't know.

42:20.960 --> 42:21.800
It's up to you.

42:24.120 --> 42:26.720
If it's up to me, then…

42:31.720 --> 42:34.280
- Exchange.
- Exchange for what?

42:36.400 --> 42:39.400
Tomorrow, I'll bring someone
home for dinner too.

42:48.840 --> 42:49.960
Do you have a girlfriend?

42:53.360 --> 42:55.760
I mean, you should tell your girlfriend

42:55.840 --> 42:58.280
about our joint rental if you have one,

42:58.360 --> 42:59.840
in case of misunderstandings.

43:00.640 --> 43:01.960
I don't have a girlfriend.

43:02.040 --> 43:04.480
But don't be too happy about it.

43:04.560 --> 43:05.800
I don't want one.

43:07.680 --> 43:08.760
Okay.

43:08.840 --> 43:10.320
So, we'll talk about it

43:10.400 --> 43:12.320
if you find a girlfriend
during our joint rental.

43:14.280 --> 43:16.840
And, of course,
I will tell you if I have a boyfriend.

43:16.920 --> 43:17.760
Not interested.

43:23.200 --> 43:24.600
Who is he going to bring back home?

43:45.440 --> 43:51.440
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

43:51.520 --> 43:53.840
He usually eats very politely.

43:53.920 --> 43:54.840
Dad,

43:54.920 --> 43:57.480
I think something's wrong with my brother.

43:58.640 --> 44:00.520
- Your brother…
- Let's toast!

44:04.400 --> 44:06.320
- Well, next…
- I have things to do. I'm going out.

44:06.920 --> 44:08.080
Where are you going
on the Spring Festival Eve?

44:09.000 --> 44:09.840
To meet a friend.

44:09.920 --> 44:11.720
What friend? Is it Jiaxu?

44:13.200 --> 44:15.880
Meet him tomorrow even if you have to.
It's the Spring Festival Eve.

44:15.960 --> 44:17.200
Come on, Ping.

44:17.280 --> 44:18.960
It's the Spring Festival Eve.

44:21.240 --> 44:23.120
It's fine. It's because you spoiled him.

44:26.640 --> 44:28.000
Why are you back?

44:28.720 --> 44:31.120
Didn't you said you wouldn't be back
until the eighth day of Spring Festival?

44:31.800 --> 44:34.240
Too many relatives at home.
There are not enough rooms.

47:19.840 --> 47:20.920
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

47:21.000 --> 47:21.960
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
